data.description: Introducing 204 North Street, a charming residence nestled in the heart of Milford. This warm and inviting home seamlessly combines comfort and style, making it an ideal choice for those in search of a cozy and well-appointed living space. The main house features three bedrooms and a full bathroom on the upper level. The main floor's inviting retreat includes a spacious living area and an eat-in kitchen, providing a perfect setting for relaxation and gatherings. The in-law/apartment, an integral part of this home, serves as the fourth bedroom and includes a second full bathroom. This versatile space can adapt to your needs, functioning either as an in-law suite or a fourth bedroom. Complete with a washer/dryer hookup, kitchenette, living room, and access to a beautiful deck, the apartment offers flexibility and convenience. Step outside to the level backyard, where you'll find a picturesque view of the Wepawaug River, adding a touch of serenity to your outdoor space. Whether you're enjoying the deck or taking in the scenery, the backyard provides a beautiful and tranquil escape. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the comfort and versatility of 204 North Street. Schedule a showing today and envision the lifestyle this charming residence has to offer. This is an as-is sale.
